Class Trigger<T extends Data>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudbus.foggatewaylib.core.Trigger<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of Data in the Store that this Trigger is observing.

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FilteredTrigger, IndividualTrigger, ProduceDataTrigger, RunProviderTrigger

    public abstract class Trigger<T extends Data>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Store.Observer<T>
    Abstract implementation of a Store.Observer that is bound to an ExecutionManager.
